WHAT IS A FOAM PARTY?

THE COOLEST SUMMER PARTY IN WESTERN MASSACHUSETTS

Foamology will drop fluffy foam up to 6 feet high on your yard, driveway, sports court, or any open area. Then, we'll crank up the tunes and watch your guests go bonkers! The best part—there is zero clean-up for you.

​

School Celebrations

Summer Camps

Preschools and Daycares

Festivals and Fairs

​

...or just for fun!
